lations 2006 reg. 24(3)(b)(iv)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["reg. 24(3)(b)(iv)"]}]}]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c2113135"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], ["C21"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], ["S. 64(3)(b) modified (1.10.2006) by ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "The Fire Safety (Scotland) Regulations 2006"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2006/456"}], ["The Fire Safety (Scotland) Regulations 2006 (S.S.I. 2006/456)"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2006/456/regulation/24/3/b/iv"}, {"title", "Go to The Fire Safety (Scotland) Regulations 2006 reg. 24(3)(b)(iv)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["reg. 24(3)(b)(iv)"]}]}]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c2113136"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], ["C22"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], ["S. 64(10) modified (1.10.2006) by ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "The Fire Safety (Scotland) Regulations 2006"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2006/456"}], ["The Fire Safety (Scotland) Regulations 2006 (S.S.I. 2006/456)"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2006/456/regulation/24/3/b/iv"}, {"title", "Go to The Fire Safety (Scotland) Regulations 2006 reg. 24(3)(b)(iv)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["reg. 24(3)(b)(iv)"]}]}]}]}]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "section-65"}], []}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP1Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegP1No"}], ["65"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Alterations notices", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Scotland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "S", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-65-1"}], ["(1)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["Where subsection (2) or (3) applies in relation to relevant premises, the enforcing authority may serve an alterations notice on the appropriate person."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-65-2"}], ["(2)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["This subsection applies where there would be a serious risk to relevant persons in respect of harm caused by fire in the relevant premises."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-65-3"}], ["(3)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["This subsection applies where—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subsection (2) does not apply; but"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if any of the changes mentioned in subsection (5) were made, it is likely that subsection (2) would apply."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-65-4"}], ["(4)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["An alterations notice is a notice requiring the appropriate person where—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["it is proposed that a change mentioned in subsection (5) be made to the relevant premises; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if made, the change would constitute a serious risk to relevant persons in respect of harm caused by fire in the relevant premises,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["to notify the enforcing authority of the change before it is made.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-65-5"}], ["(5)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["Those changes are—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change to the relevant premises;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change to the services, fittings or equipment on the relevant premises;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-5-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an increase in the quantities of dangerous substances which are present on the relevant premises; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-65-5-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change in the use to which the relevant premises are put (or, where they are put to more than one use, a use to which they are put)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-65-6"}], ["(6)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["An enforcing authority may 